entityDefs.name: Referenceable
entityDefs.description: Base class for everything in Atlan that can be referenced by qualifiedName.

attributeDefs.name: qualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name for this asset. This is typically a concatenation of the asset's name onto its parent's qualifiedName. This must be unique across all assets of the same type.

attributeDefs.name: replicatedFrom
attributeDefs.description: Unused. List of servers where this entity is replicated from.

attributeDefs.name: replicatedTo
attributeDefs.description: Unused. List of servers where this entity is replicated to.

attributeDefs.name: name
attributeDefs.description: Name of this asset. Fallback for display purposes, if displayName is empty.

attributeDefs.name: displayName
attributeDefs.description: Human-readable name of this asset used for display purposes (in user interface).

attributeDefs.name: description
attributeDefs.description: Description of this asset, for example as crawled from a source. Fallback for display purposes, if userDescription is empty.

attributeDefs.name: userDescription
attributeDefs.description: Description of this asset, as provided by a user. If present, this will be used for the description in user interface.

attributeDefs.name: tenantId
attributeDefs.description: Name of the Atlan workspace in which this asset exists.

attributeDefs.name: certificateStatus
attributeDefs.description: Status of this asset's certification.

attributeDefs.name: certificateStatusMessage
attributeDefs.description: Human-readable descriptive message used to provide further detail to certificateStatus.

attributeDefs.name: certificateUpdatedBy
attributeDefs.description: Name of the user who last updated the certification of this asset.

attributeDefs.name: certificateUpdatedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which the certification was last updated, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: announcementTitle
attributeDefs.description: Brief title for the announcement on this asset. Required when announcementType is specified.

attributeDefs.name: announcementMessage
attributeDefs.description: Detailed message to include in the announcement on this asset.

attributeDefs.name: announcementType
attributeDefs.description: Type of announcement on this asset.

attributeDefs.name: announcementUpdatedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which the announcement was last updated, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: announcementUpdatedBy
attributeDefs.description: Name of the user who last updated the announcement.

attributeDefs.name: ownerUsers
attributeDefs.description: List of users who own this asset.

attributeDefs.name: ownerGroups
attributeDefs.description: List of groups who own this asset.

attributeDefs.name: adminUsers
attributeDefs.description: List of users who administer this asset. (This is only used for certain asset types.)

attributeDefs.name: adminGroups
attributeDefs.description: List of groups who administer this asset. (This is only used for certain asset types.)

attributeDefs.name: viewerUsers
attributeDefs.description: List of users who can view assets contained in a collection. (This is only used for certain asset types.)

attributeDefs.name: viewerGroups
attributeDefs.description: List of groups who can view assets contained in a collection. (This is only used for certain asset types.)

attributeDefs.name: connectorName
attributeDefs.description: Type of the connector through which this asset is accessible.

attributeDefs.name: connectionName
attributeDefs.description: Simple name of the connection through which this asset is accessible.

attributeDefs.name: connectionQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the connection through which this asset is accessible.

attributeDefs.name: __hasLineage
attributeDefs.description: Whether this asset has lineage (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: isDiscoverable
attributeDefs.description: Whether this asset is discoverable through the UI (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: isEditable
attributeDefs.description: Whether this asset can be edited in the UI (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: subType
attributeDefs.description: Subtype of this asset.

attributeDefs.name: viewScore
attributeDefs.description: View score for this asset.

attributeDefs.name: popularityScore
attributeDefs.description: Popularity score for this asset.

attributeDefs.name: sourceOwners
attributeDefs.description: List of owners of this asset, in the source system.

attributeDefs.name: sourceCreatedBy
attributeDefs.description: Name of the user who created this asset, in the source system.

attributeDefs.name: sourceCreatedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which this asset was created in the source system, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: sourceUpdatedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which this asset was last updated in the source system, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: sourceUpdatedBy
attributeDefs.description: Name of the user who last updated this asset, in the source system.

attributeDefs.name: sourceURL
attributeDefs.description: URL to the resource within the source application, used to create a button to view this asset in the source application.

attributeDefs.name: sourceEmbedURL
attributeDefs.description: URL to create an embed for a resource (for example, an image of a dashboard) within Atlan.

attributeDefs.name: lastSyncWorkflowName
attributeDefs.description: Name of the crawler that last synchronized this asset.

attributeDefs.name: lastSyncRunAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which this asset was last crawled, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: lastSyncRun
attributeDefs.description: Name of the last run of the crawler that last synchronized this asset.

attributeDefs.name: adminRoles
attributeDefs.description: List of roles who administer this asset. (This is only used for Connection assets.)

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadCount
attributeDefs.description: Total count of all read operations at source.

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadUserCount
attributeDefs.description: Total number of unique users that read data from asset.

attributeDefs.name: sourceLastReadAt
attributeDefs.description: Timestamp of most recent read operation.

attributeDefs.name: lastRowChangedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) of the last operation that inserted, updated, or deleted rows, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: sourceTotalCost
attributeDefs.description: Total cost of all operations at source.

attributeDefs.name: sourceCostUnit
attributeDefs.description: The unit of measure for sourceTotalCost.

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadQueryCost
attributeDefs.description: Total cost of read queries at source.

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadRecentUserList
attributeDefs.description: List of usernames of the most recent users who read this asset.

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadRecentUserRecordList
attributeDefs.description: List of usernames with extra insights for the most recent users who read this asset.

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadTopUserList
attributeDefs.description: List of usernames of the users who read this asset the most.

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadTopUserRecordList
attributeDefs.description: List of usernames with extra insights for the users who read this asset the most.

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadPopularQueryRecordList
attributeDefs.description: List of the most popular queries that accessed this asset.

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadExpensiveQueryRecordList
attributeDefs.description: List of the most expensive queries that accessed this asset.

attributeDefs.name: sourceReadSlowQueryRecordList
attributeDefs.description: List of the slowest queries that accessed this asset.

attributeDefs.name: sourceQueryComputeCostList
attributeDefs.description: List of most expensive warehouse names.

attributeDefs.name: sourceQueryComputeCostRecordList
attributeDefs.description: List of most expensive warehouses with extra insights.

attributeDefs.name: dbtQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtAlias
attributeDefs.description: Alias of this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtMeta
attributeDefs.description: Metadata for this asset in dbt, specifically everything under the 'meta' key in the dbt object.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtUniqueId
attributeDefs.description: Unique identifier of this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtAccountName
attributeDefs.description: Name of the account in which this asset exists in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtProjectName
attributeDefs.description: Name of the project in which this asset exists in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtPackageName
attributeDefs.description: Name of the package in which this asset exists in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobName
attributeDefs.description: Name of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobSchedule
attributeDefs.description: Schedule of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobStatus
attributeDefs.description: Status of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtTestStatus
attributeDefs.description: All associated dbt test statuses.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobScheduleCronHumanized
attributeDefs.description: Human-readable cron schedule of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRun
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which the job that materialized this asset in dbt last ran, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunUrl
attributeDefs.description: URL of the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunCreatedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which the job that materialized this asset in dbt was last created, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunUpdatedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which the job that materialized this asset in dbt was last updated, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunDequedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which the job that materialized this asset in dbt was dequeued, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunStartedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which the job that materialized this asset in dbt was started running, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunTotalDuration
attributeDefs.description: Total duration of the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunTotalDurationHumanized
attributeDefs.description: Human-readable total duration of the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunQueuedDuration
attributeDefs.description: Total duration the job that materialized this asset in dbt spent being queued.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunQueuedDurationHumanized
attributeDefs.description: Human-readable total duration of the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt spend being queued.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunRunDuration
attributeDefs.description: Run duration of the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunRunDurationHumanized
attributeDefs.description: Human-readable run duration of the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunGitBranch
attributeDefs.description: Branch in git from which the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt ran.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunGitSha
attributeDefs.description: SHA hash in git for the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunStatusMessage
attributeDefs.description: Status message of the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunOwnerThreadId
attributeDefs.description: Thread ID of the owner of the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunExecutedByThreadId
attributeDefs.description: Thread ID of the user who executed the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunArtifactsSaved
attributeDefs.description: Whether artifacts were saved from the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunArtifactS3Path
attributeDefs.description: Path in S3 to the artifacts saved from the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunHasDocsGenerated
attributeDefs.description: Whether docs were generated from the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunHasSourcesGenerated
attributeDefs.description: Whether sources were generated from the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobLastRunNotificationsSent
attributeDefs.description: Whether notifications were sent from the last run of the job that materialized this asset in dbt (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobNextRun
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) when the next run of the job that materializes this asset in dbt is scheduled.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtJobNextRunHumanized
attributeDefs.description: Human-readable time when the next run of the job that materializes this asset in dbt is scheduled.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtEnvironmentName
attributeDefs.description: Name of the environment in which this asset is materialized in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtEnvironmentDbtVersion
attributeDefs.description: Version of the environment in which this asset is materialized in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtTags
attributeDefs.description: List of tags attached to this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtSemanticLayerProxyUrl
attributeDefs.description: URL of the semantic layer proxy for this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: assetDbtSourceFreshnessCriteria
attributeDefs.description: Freshness criteria for the source of this asset in dbt.

attributeDefs.name: sampleDataUrl
attributeDefs.description: URL for sample data for this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetTags
attributeDefs.description: List of tags attached to this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcIncidentNames
attributeDefs.description: List of Monte Carlo incident names attached to this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcIncidentQualifiedNames
attributeDefs.description: List of unique Monte Carlo incident names attached to this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcMonitorNames
attributeDefs.description: List of Monte Carlo monitor names attached to this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcMonitorQualifiedNames
attributeDefs.description: List of unique Monte Carlo monitor names attached to this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcMonitorStatuses
attributeDefs.description: Statuses of all associated Monte Carlo monitors.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcMonitorTypes
attributeDefs.description: Types of all associated Monte Carlo monitors.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcMonitorScheduleTypes
attributeDefs.description: Schedules of all associated Monte Carlo monitors.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcIncidentTypes
attributeDefs.description: List of Monte Carlo incident types associated with this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcIncidentSubTypes
attributeDefs.description: List of Monte Carlo incident sub-types associated with this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcIncidentSeverities
attributeDefs.description: List of Monte Carlo incident severities associated with this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcIncidentStates
attributeDefs.description: List of Monte Carlo incident states associated with this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetMcLastSyncRunAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which this asset was last synced from Monte Carlo.

attributeDefs.name: starredBy
attributeDefs.description: Users who have starred this asset.

attributeDefs.name: starredDetailsList
attributeDefs.description: List of usernames with extra information of the users who have starred an asset.

attributeDefs.name: starredCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of users who have starred this asset.

attributeDefs.name: assetSodaDQStatus
attributeDefs.description: Status of data quality from Soda.

attributeDefs.name: assetSodaCheckCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of checks done via Soda.

attributeDefs.name: assetSodaCheckStatuses
attributeDefs.description: All associated Soda check statuses.

attributeDefs.name: assetIcon
attributeDefs.description: Name of the icon to use for this asset. (Only applies to glossaries, currently.)

entityDefs.name: Catalog
entityDefs.description: Base class for catalog assets. Catalog assets include any asset that can participate in lineage.

attributeDefs.name: queryCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of times this asset has been queried.

attributeDefs.name: queryUserCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of unique users who have queried this asset.

attributeDefs.name: queryUserMap
attributeDefs.description: Map of unique users who have queried this asset to the number of times they have queried it.

attributeDefs.name: queryCountUpdatedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which the query count was last updated, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: databaseName
attributeDefs.description: Simple name of the database in which this SQL asset exists, or empty if it does not exist within a database.

attributeDefs.name: databaseQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the database in which this SQL asset exists, or empty if it does not exist within a database.

attributeDefs.name: schemaName
attributeDefs.description: Simple name of the schema in which this SQL asset exists, or empty if it does not exist within a schema.

attributeDefs.name: schemaQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the schema in which this SQL asset exists, or empty if it does not exist within a schema.

attributeDefs.name: tableName
attributeDefs.description: Simple name of the table in which this SQL asset exists, or empty if it does not exist within a table.

attributeDefs.name: tableQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the table in which this SQL asset exists, or empty if it does not exist within a table.

attributeDefs.name: viewName
attributeDefs.description: Simple name of the view in which this SQL asset exists, or empty if it does not exist within a view.

attributeDefs.name: viewQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the view in which this SQL asset exists, or empty if it does not exist within a view.

attributeDefs.name: isProfiled
attributeDefs.description: Whether this asset has been profiled (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: lastProfiledAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which this asset was last profiled, in milliseconds.

entityDefs.name: Column
entityDefs.description: Instance of a column in Atlan.

attributeDefs.name: dataType
attributeDefs.description: Data type of values in this column.

attributeDefs.name: subDataType
attributeDefs.description: Sub-data type of this column.

attributeDefs.name: order
attributeDefs.description: Order (position) in which this column appears in the table (starting at 1).

attributeDefs.name: nestedColumnCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of columns nested within this (STRUCT or NESTED) column.

attributeDefs.name: isPartition
attributeDefs.description: Whether this column is a partition column (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: partitionOrder
attributeDefs.description: Order (position) of this partition column in the table.

attributeDefs.name: isClustered
attributeDefs.description: Whether this column is a clustered column (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: isPrimary
attributeDefs.description: When true, this column is the primary key for the table.

attributeDefs.name: isForeign
attributeDefs.description: When true, this column is a foreign key to another table. NOTE: this must be true when using the foreignKeyTo relationship to specify columns that refer to this column as a foreign key.

attributeDefs.name: isIndexed
attributeDefs.description: When true, this column is indexed in the database.

attributeDefs.name: isSort
attributeDefs.description: Whether this column is a sort column (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: isDist
attributeDefs.description: Whether this column is a distribution column (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: isPinned
attributeDefs.description: Whether this column is pinned (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: pinnedBy
attributeDefs.description: User who pinned this column.

attributeDefs.name: pinnedAt
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) at which this column was pinned, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: precision
attributeDefs.description: Total number of digits allowed, when the dataType is numeric.

attributeDefs.name: defaultValue
attributeDefs.description: Default value for this column.

attributeDefs.name: isNullable
attributeDefs.description: When true, the values in this column can be null.

attributeDefs.name: numericScale
attributeDefs.description: Number of digits allowed to the right of the decimal point.

attributeDefs.name: maxLength
attributeDefs.description: Maximum length of a value in this column.

attributeDefs.name: validations
attributeDefs.description: Validations for this column.

attributeDefs.name: parentColumnQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the column this column is nested within, for STRUCT and NESTED columns.

attributeDefs.name: parentColumnName
attributeDefs.description: Simple name of the column this column is nested within, for STRUCT and NESTED columns.

attributeDefs.name: columnDistinctValuesCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows that contain distinct values.

attributeDefs.name: columnDistinctValuesCountLong
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows that contain distinct values.

attributeDefs.name: columnHistogram
attributeDefs.description: List of values in a histogram that represents the contents of this column.

attributeDefs.name: columnMax
attributeDefs.description: Greatest value in a numeric column.

attributeDefs.name: columnMin
attributeDefs.description: Least value in a numeric column.

attributeDefs.name: columnMean
attributeDefs.description: Arithmetic mean of the values in a numeric column.

attributeDefs.name: columnSum
attributeDefs.description: Calculated sum of the values in a numeric column.

attributeDefs.name: columnMedian
attributeDefs.description: Calculated median of the values in a numeric column.

attributeDefs.name: columnStandardDeviation
attributeDefs.description: Calculated standard deviation of the values in a numeric column.

attributeDefs.name: columnUniqueValuesCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows in which a value in this column appears only once.

attributeDefs.name: columnUniqueValuesCountLong
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows in which a value in this column appears only once.

attributeDefs.name: columnAverage
attributeDefs.description: Average value in this column.

attributeDefs.name: columnAverageLength
attributeDefs.description: Average length of values in a string column.

attributeDefs.name: columnDuplicateValuesCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows that contain duplicate values.

attributeDefs.name: columnDuplicateValuesCountLong
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows that contain duplicate values.

attributeDefs.name: columnMaximumStringLength
attributeDefs.description: Length of the longest value in a string column.

attributeDefs.name: columnMaxs
attributeDefs.description: List of the greatest values in a column.

attributeDefs.name: columnMinimumStringLength
attributeDefs.description: Length of the shortest value in a string column.

attributeDefs.name: columnMins
attributeDefs.description: List of the least values in a column.

attributeDefs.name: columnMissingValuesCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows in a column that do not contain content.

attributeDefs.name: columnMissingValuesCountLong
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows in a column that do not contain content.

attributeDefs.name: columnMissingValuesPercentage
attributeDefs.description: Percentage of rows in a column that do not contain content.

attributeDefs.name: columnUniquenessPercentage
attributeDefs.description: Ratio indicating how unique data in this column is: 0 indicates that all values are the same, 100 indicates that all values in this column are unique.

attributeDefs.name: columnVariance
attributeDefs.description: Calculated variance of the values in a numeric column.

attributeDefs.name: columnTopValues
attributeDefs.description: List of top values in this column.

attributeDefs.name: columnDepthLevel
attributeDefs.description: Level of nesting of this column, used for STRUCT and NESTED columns.

entityDefs.name: GuacamoleColumn
entityDefs.description: Specialized form of a column specific to Guacamole.

attributeDefs.name: guacamoleWidth
attributeDefs.description: Maximum size of a Guacamole column.

attributeDefs.name: guacamoleConceptualized
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) when this column was imagined, in milliseconds.

entityDefs.name: Table
entityDefs.description: Instance of a database table in Atlan.

attributeDefs.name: columnCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of columns in this table.

attributeDefs.name: rowCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows in this table.

attributeDefs.name: sizeBytes
attributeDefs.description: Size of this table, in bytes.

attributeDefs.name: alias
attributeDefs.description: Alias for this table.

attributeDefs.name: isTemporary
attributeDefs.description: Whether this table is temporary (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: isQueryPreview
attributeDefs.description: Whether preview queries are allowed for this table (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: queryPreviewConfig
attributeDefs.description: Configuration for preview queries.

attributeDefs.name: externalLocation
attributeDefs.description: External location of this table, for example: an S3 object location.

attributeDefs.name: externalLocationRegion
attributeDefs.description: Region of the external location of this table, for example: S3 region.

attributeDefs.name: externalLocationFormat
attributeDefs.description: Format of the external location of this table, for example: JSON, CSV, PARQUET, etc.

attributeDefs.name: isPartitioned
attributeDefs.description: Whether this table is partitioned (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: partitionStrategy
attributeDefs.description: Partition strategy for this table.

attributeDefs.name: partitionCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of partitions in this table.

attributeDefs.name: partitionList
attributeDefs.description: List of partitions in this table.

entityDefs.name: GuacamoleTable
entityDefs.description: Specialized form of a table specific to Guacamole.

attributeDefs.name: guacamoleSize
attributeDefs.description: Consolidated quantification metric spanning number of columns, rows, and sparsity of population.

attributeDefs.name: guacamoleTemperature
attributeDefs.description: Rough measure of the IOPS allocated to the table's processing.

attributeDefs.name: guacamoleArchived
attributeDefs.description: Whether this table is currently archived (true) or not (false).

entityDefs.name: Process
entityDefs.description: Instance of a lineage process in Atlan.

attributeDefs.name: inputs
attributeDefs.description: Assets that are inputs to this process.

attributeDefs.name: outputs
attributeDefs.description: Assets that are outputs from this process.

attributeDefs.name: code
attributeDefs.description: Code that ran within the process.

attributeDefs.name: sql
attributeDefs.description: SQL query that ran to produce the outputs.

attributeDefs.name: ast
attributeDefs.description: Parsed AST of the code or SQL statements that describe the logic of this process.

relationshipAttributeDefs.name: outputs
relationshipAttributeDefs.description: Assets that are outputs from this process.

relationshipAttributeDefs.name: inputs
relationshipAttributeDefs.description: Assets that are inputs to this process.

entityDefs.name: MaterialisedView
entityDefs.description: Instance of a materialized view in Atlan.

attributeDefs.name: refreshMode
attributeDefs.description: Refresh mode for this materialized view.

attributeDefs.name: refreshMethod
attributeDefs.description: Refresh method for this materialized view.

attributeDefs.name: staleness
attributeDefs.description: Staleness of this materialized view.

attributeDefs.name: staleSinceDate
attributeDefs.description: Time (epoch) from which this materialized view is stale, in milliseconds.

attributeDefs.name: columnCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of columns in this materialized view.

attributeDefs.name: rowCount
attributeDefs.description: Number of rows in this materialized view.

attributeDefs.name: sizeBytes
attributeDefs.description: Size of this materialized view, in bytes.

attributeDefs.name: isQueryPreview
attributeDefs.description: Whether it's possible to run a preview query on this materialized view (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: queryPreviewConfig
attributeDefs.description: Configuration for the query preview of this materialized view.

attributeDefs.name: alias
attributeDefs.description: Alias for this materialized view.

attributeDefs.name: isTemporary
attributeDefs.description: Whether this materialized view is temporary (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: definition
attributeDefs.description: SQL definition of this materialized view.

entityDefs.name: Query
entityDefs.description: Instance of a query in Atlan.

attributeDefs.name: rawQuery
attributeDefs.description: Deprecated. See 'longRawQuery' instead.

attributeDefs.name: longRawQuery
attributeDefs.description: Raw SQL query string.

attributeDefs.name: defaultSchemaQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the default schema to use for this query.

attributeDefs.name: defaultDatabaseQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the default database to use for this query.

attributeDefs.name: variablesSchemaBase64
attributeDefs.description: Base64-encoded string of the variables to use in this query.

attributeDefs.name: isPrivate
attributeDefs.description: Whether this query is private (true) or shared (false).

attributeDefs.name: isSqlSnippet
attributeDefs.description: Whether this query is a SQL snippet (true) or not (false).

attributeDefs.name: parentQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the parent collection or folder in which this query exists.

attributeDefs.name: collectionQualifiedName
attributeDefs.description: Unique name of the collection in which this query exists.

attributeDefs.name: isVisualQuery
attributeDefs.description: Whether this query is a visual query (true) or not (false).
